    Hussain Yusuf's Post

    Hussain Yusuf is with Hauwa Alhassan.
    · Yesterday at 4:26pm ·

    This is a very special month for my mother Hauwa Alhassan, may God Bless Her! Ameen!!!Today is Mother’s Day because it’s my Mother’s Birthday! Just a few days ago this country celebrated a special day to all mothers but to all mothers just to let you know we as your children cherish Mothers Day everyday! This past weekend my mom accomplished one of her major goals and graduated with a Bachelors degree from St Mary’s University in Child Care at the top of her class. “Difficult... roads lead to beautiful destinations” Despite the the big rocks thrown in her way the past three years, my mother kicked those rocks to the side and contued her journey to reach one of her many goals. When the room was dark, it is her spirit and faith in God that lights her path to continue doing what she does best! The best part of this month is that it’s also Ramadan for Muslims. A time and month where we give back, help those in need, fasting for success! Fasting for the ultimate prize! The smile on Gods face!❤️ Happy Birthday Mama and May God continue to pave that path you are yearning for and may Allah bless you and Baba with everything that you ask for in this life and after! Ameen!!!
